node.text:
GIVEAWAY 🎉 Who's in for a 2 night coastal escape to San Diego to dine, surf, relax, and more! 
Enter To Win: Tag who you'd take with, and Follow @hyattregencylajolla & @LosAngelesBucketList 

Winner will receive a 2 night stay, dinner for 2 in DRIFT eat + drink, breakfast for 2 in Market La Jolla, private poolside cabana, & surfboard rentals from Surf Divas. 

Close to scenic beaches, hiking, area attractions and upscale dining & shopping, the recently revamped @hyattregencylajolla draws inspo from nearby La Jolla Cove. Visit our link-in-bio to book and for more info! #Partner #BucketListers 
-- Giveaway not affiliated with IG, value $1100, will end on 11:59 EST 8/5. Must be +21. Selection details & terms: bit.ly/bucketlistterms
